g.title: Awaiting first byte of network buffer
**Invariants**: - Delimiter: single space (0x20) - Terminator: CRLF or LF
**Action**: - Normalize key to lowercase - Strip OWS from value
**Invariants**: - Host header must exist (1.1) - Content-Length must be integer
